# DENTAL PRO MODULAR - ARCHITECTURE & COMPONENT DOCUMENTATION

## OVERVIEW

This version of the dental scheduling application is built with **true modularity** - every component, utility, and module can be used independently or together. No monolithic files. Everything is organized by concern and feature.

**Key Benefit:** Take any component and use it in another project without modification.

---

