### 2. CARD COMPONENT (components/cards/)

**File:** `cards.js` + `cards.css`  
**Purpose:** Display information in a card container

**Constructor Options:**
```javascript
{
  title: 'Card Title',
  subtitle: 'Optional subtitle',
  content: 'Card content HTML',
  image: 'url/path',
  badge: 'Badge text',
  badgeColor: '#2180CE',
  onClick: function() {},
  actions: [ { label: 'Edit', onClick: fn }, ... ]
}
```

**Usage Examples:**
```javascript
// Doctor card
const doctorCard = new Card({
  title: 'Dr. Sarah Johnson',
  subtitle: 'General Dentistry',
  badge: 'Working',
  badgeColor: '#50C878',
  content: `
    <p>License: DT-2020-001</p>
    <p>Today: 6 appointments</p>
  `,
  actions: [
    { label: 'Edit', onClick: handleEdit },
    { label: 'Schedule', onClick: handleSchedule }
  ],
  onClick: handleCardClick
});

// Metric card
