## ANDROID OPTIMIZATION

### Touch-Friendly Interactions

**1. Button Sizing (48x48px minimum)**
```css
.btn-touch {
  min-height: 48px;
  min-width: 48px;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  font-size: 16px;  /* Prevents zoom on iOS */
  touch-action: manipulation;
}
```

**2. Spacing Between Elements**
```css
.touch-spacing {
  margin: 8px;  /* Minimum spacing between tappable elements */
}
```

**3. Haptic Feedback (if available)**
```javascript
function triggerHaptic() {
  if (navigator.vibrate) {
    navigator.vibrate(10);  // 10ms vibration
  }
}
```

**4. Swipe Detection**
```javascript
let touchStartX = 0;
let touchEndX = 0;

document.addEventListener('touchstart', e => {
  touchStartX = e.changedTouches[0].screenX;
});

document.addEventListener('touchend', e => {
  touchEndX = e.changedTouches[0].screenX;
  if (touchEndX < touchStartX - 50) {
    handleSwipeLeft();
  }
});
```

### Android-Specific CSS

```css
/* android-specific.css */

/* Optimize for Android Chrome */
body {
  -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  user-select: none;
  -webkit-user-select: none;
}

/* Touch ripple effect */
.ripple {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.ripple::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  border-radius: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0);
  animation: ripple 0.6s ease-out;
}

@keyframes ripple {
  to {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(4);
    opacity: 0;
  }
}

/* Bottom sheet modal for Android */
.modal-android {
  animation: slideUp 0.3s ease-out;
}

@keyframes slideUp {
  from {
    transform: translateY(100%);
  }
  to {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}

/* Responsive text for mobile */
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  body {
    font-size: 16px;  /* Prevents zoom on iOS input focus */
  }
}
```

