## DEVELOPMENT WORKFLOW

### Adding a New Component

1. **Create component folder:**
   ```
   components/my-component/
   â”œâ”€â”€ my-component.js
   â””â”€â”€ my-component.css
   ```

2. **Implement component class:**
   ```javascript
   export class MyComponent {
     constructor(options) {
       // Store options
     }

     render() {
       // Return DOM element
     }
   }
   ```

3. **Add styling:**
   ```css
   /* my-component.css */
   .my-component {
     /* styles */
   }
   ```

4. **Export from index:**
   ```javascript
   export { MyComponent } from './my-component/my-component.js';
   ```

### Adding a New Module

1. **Create module folder:**
   ```
   modules/my-module/
   â”œâ”€â”€ my-module.js
   â”œâ”€â”€ my-module.html
   â””â”€â”€ my-module.css
   ```

2. **Implement module class:**
   ```javascript
   export class MyModule {
     constructor(dataStore) {
       this.dataStore = dataStore;
     }

     render() {
       // Return module UI
     }
   }
   ```

3. **Register in navigation:**
   ```javascript
   navigation.items.push({
     label: 'My Module',
     id: 'my-module'
   });
   ```

