## PERFORMANCE TIPS

### 1. Lazy Load Modules
```javascript
const modules = {
  dashboard: null,
  doctors: null
};

async function loadModule(moduleName) {
  if (!modules[moduleName]) {
    const { [moduleName]: Module } = await import(`./modules/${moduleName}/${moduleName}.js`);
    modules[moduleName] = new Module(dataStore);
  }
  return modules[moduleName];
}
```

### 2. Debounce Search/Filter
```javascript
function debounce(func, wait) {
  let timeout;
  return function(...args) {
    clearTimeout(timeout);
    timeout = setTimeout(() => func(...args), wait);
  };
}

const handleSearch = debounce(performSearch, 300);
```

### 3. Minimize Reflows
```javascript
// Bad - causes multiple reflows
for (let i = 0; i < 100; i++) {
  element.style.width = i + 'px';
}

// Good - single reflow
const clone = element.cloneNode(true);
// ... make changes ...
element.replaceWith(clone);
```

### 4. Use CSS Transforms for Animations
```css
/* GPU accelerated */
.animated {
  animation: slide 0.3s ease-out;
}

@keyframes slide {
  from {
    transform: translateX(-100%);
  }
  to {
    transform: translateX(0);
  }
}
```

