## TESTING COMPONENTS

### Testing Button Component

```javascript
// Test button rendering
const button = new Button({
  label: 'Test',
  onClick: () => { clicked = true; }
});

const el = button.render();
assert(el.textContent === 'Test');

// Simulate click
el.click();
assert(clicked === true);
```

### Testing Modal Component

```javascript
const modal = new Modal({
  title: 'Test Modal',
  content: 'Test content',
  buttons: [{ label: 'OK', onClick: () => { ok = true; } }]
});

const el = modal.render();
assert(el.querySelector('.modal-title').textContent === 'Test Modal');

// Click button
el.querySelector('button').click();
assert(ok === true);
```

