## SUMMARY

This modular architecture gives you:

âœ… **Reusable Components** - Use any component standalone  
âœ… **Organized Code** - Clear file structure and separation of concerns  
âœ… **Easy Maintenance** - Change one file without affecting others  
âœ… **Team-Friendly** - Different developers can work on different components  
âœ… **Framework Agnostic** - Can integrate with React, Vue, Angular, etc.  
âœ… **Mobile-First** - Android optimization built-in  
âœ… **Scalable** - Add new modules without refactoring  

You can now take `components/buttons.js` and use it in a completely different project without any changes!
